column2: Jane Kahan Mera Jigar Gaya Ji
Jane Bhi De Chhod Yeh Bahana
Piya Piya Piya Mora Jiya Pukare
Chana Jor Garam Babu Main Laya
Kahin Pe Nigahen Kahin Pe Nishana
Gori Gori Raat Hai Taron Ki
Yeh Desh Hai Veer Jawanon Ka
Aaye Hai Door Se Milne Huzoor Se
Ik Pardesi Mera Dil Le Gaya
Piya Piya Na Lage Mora Jiya
Mohabbat Ka Haath Jawani Ka Palla
Pyar Par Bas To Nahin Hai
Raat Bhar Ka Hai Mehman Andhera
Maut Kabhi Bhi Mil Sakti Hai
Nazron Ke Tir Mare Kas Kas
Aap Yun Hi Agar Humse Milte Rahe
Dekho Bijli Dole Bin Badal Ki
Ankhon Se Jo Utri Hai Dil Men
Kahin Na Kahin Dil Lagana Padega
Yeh Hai Reshmi Zulfon Ka Andhera
Yehi Woh Jaga Hai Yehi Woh Fazayen
Na Jane Kyon Hamare Dil Ko
Ek Tu Hai Piya Jis Pe Dil
Sau Saal Jiyo Tum Jaan Meri
Zulf Lahrai To Sawan Ka Mahina
